WEBVTT

00:08.320 --> 00:09.800
Miao An Su defended you.

00:10.520 --> 00:12.040
She said that at the start of the year,

00:12.120 --> 00:14.600
you said that maritime trade
had reached its peak,

00:14.680 --> 00:16.920
and that it was time to pull out
of the business in Futing.

00:17.000 --> 00:20.520
It's as if you predicted my uncle's death.

00:20.600 --> 00:21.680
Of course not.

00:22.840 --> 00:24.160
In business,

00:25.000 --> 00:27.120
it's all about buying low
and selling high.

00:28.200 --> 00:29.760
After the victory at Zhou Island,

00:29.840 --> 00:32.759
maritime trade flourished,
and everyone rushed to claim a share.

00:32.840 --> 00:34.680
Of course I had
to seek other opportunities.

00:43.720 --> 00:45.280
Dou Zhao,

00:45.360 --> 00:48.400
your heartbeat is all over the place.

00:50.160 --> 00:51.160
I can tell

00:52.720 --> 00:55.280
you're hiding something from me,
something that involves me.

00:56.920 --> 00:58.680
Why won't you tell me?

01:01.200 --> 01:02.600
Say it!

01:03.560 --> 01:04.560
I…

01:15.960 --> 01:17.320
If I survive,

01:17.960 --> 01:19.480
I promise I'll explain everything.

01:26.080 --> 01:27.240
I'll trust you one more time.

01:32.800 --> 01:35.360
I'm Ji Yong, a secretary from the
Irrigation and Transportation Office.

01:35.440 --> 01:37.280
The Miao family borrowed funds to build
ships but has yet to repay their debts.

01:37.960 --> 01:40.080
Under the orders of
the Futing Provincial Administration,

01:40.160 --> 01:41.880
I am here to investigate the case

01:41.960 --> 01:44.360
and summon Dou Zhao
and Miao An Su for questioning.

03:07.360 --> 03:09.280
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL "BLOSSOM"
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

03:15.520 --> 03:16.880
Young Lady!

03:21.840 --> 03:23.800
-They're on our side.
-The act has to be convincing.

03:24.480 --> 03:27.480
Young Lady Zhao,
you have quite the connections.

03:28.080 --> 03:30.360
People from all over the land
would risk their lives for you.

03:31.040 --> 03:32.480
Too bad you ended up in my hands.

03:33.240 --> 03:35.840
No one's getting the chance to
play the hero and save the damsel.

03:38.680 --> 03:39.880
Wrong.

03:40.480 --> 03:43.960
You're overstepping your authority here.
Now you're in my hands.

03:45.800 --> 03:47.560
You're a mere seventh-ranked
official from the Ministry of Works,

03:47.640 --> 03:49.920
yet you're meddling in a case under the
jurisdiction of Maritime Trade Office.

03:50.600 --> 03:51.960
Who's really overstepping
their authority here?

03:52.040 --> 03:54.880
The Provincial Administration
oversees all regional matters.

03:54.960 --> 03:58.160
I'm acting under direct orders,
legally and by the book.

03:58.240 --> 03:59.640
You, on the other hand,

04:00.200 --> 04:02.800
were trying to coerce a confession.

04:03.880 --> 04:05.520
You really think you can stop me

04:06.520 --> 04:07.600
from solving the case?

04:07.680 --> 04:10.520
Oh, I haven't even started. Watch this.

04:12.520 --> 04:13.640
-Ji Yong!
-Lord Ji!

04:13.720 --> 04:15.360
My Lord, someone's injured.

04:16.160 --> 04:18.399
You've assaulted a court official.

04:18.480 --> 04:20.560
You'll be charged and thrown into prison!

04:20.640 --> 04:21.920
Careful, Young Lady!

04:24.160 --> 04:25.160
Let them fight.

04:25.880 --> 04:27.560
It's even better if he kills someone.

04:27.640 --> 04:29.080
The blame won't fall on me anyway.

04:30.760 --> 04:32.200
Song Mo, stop!

04:32.760 --> 04:34.800
-Young Lady, careful!
-I've seen enough. Let's go.

04:34.880 --> 04:35.960
Let go!

04:37.400 --> 04:39.000
-Support me.
-Yes, sir.

04:43.840 --> 04:46.040
Good thing I came prepared
to fool Ding Wei.

04:46.680 --> 04:48.360
You knew we were acting?

04:48.440 --> 04:51.280
I heard from the jailer that Lord Song
was interrogating you personally.

04:51.360 --> 04:53.840
I figured he wouldn't be that stupid,

04:53.920 --> 04:56.040
and that he could see through
Ding Wei's setup.

04:57.800 --> 04:59.160
I could never compare to you, Lord Ji.

04:59.840 --> 05:01.120
Wherever you go,

05:01.200 --> 05:02.760
you're ready to sacrifice
everything for the lady.

05:11.480 --> 05:13.160
They're still watching. Quick, insult me

05:20.440 --> 05:21.680
You scoundrel!

05:21.760 --> 05:23.760
What, you big mantis? Kill me if you dare!

05:30.880 --> 05:32.520
Looks like this is real.

05:35.160 --> 05:37.480
Order our men to wait a little longer.

05:37.560 --> 05:39.240
Let them finish their fight.
We'll clean up the mess afterward.

05:39.320 --> 05:41.240
Yes, sir.

05:43.520 --> 05:45.160
-Kill me if you dare!
-Don't push me!

05:45.240 --> 05:46.280
Do it!

05:47.080 --> 05:48.040
They're gone.

05:48.120 --> 05:49.200
All right, let go.

05:49.800 --> 05:50.800
They're gone.

05:52.200 --> 05:53.240
Thank you both for your help.

05:53.840 --> 05:55.800
Su Lan, go check on Su Su.

05:56.400 --> 05:58.120
Keep watch outside.
Alert us if anyone comes.

05:58.200 --> 05:59.160
Yes, Young Lady.

06:02.680 --> 06:05.120
It's going to leave a scar
if you don't get it treated.

06:07.200 --> 06:08.440
You've applied medicine?

06:12.760 --> 06:14.840
Military medicine is only good
for stopping bleeding.

06:15.440 --> 06:17.240
This, however,
is a premium healing ointment.

06:25.480 --> 06:28.400
I've always heard that you're brilliant
but emotionally detached.

06:30.160 --> 06:32.920
Yet here you are, risking life
and limb for Young Lady Zhao.

06:33.720 --> 06:34.720
You're quite the romantic after all.

06:37.640 --> 06:40.280
Little dreamer and I have known
each other since we were little.

06:40.360 --> 06:42.800
She's my soulmate,
so of course she's special to me.

06:43.480 --> 06:45.320
It's a bond you could never understand.

06:47.080 --> 06:48.120
Come.

06:51.880 --> 06:53.360
Something just feels off
the more I think about it.

06:54.040 --> 06:55.760
How could we let Lord Ji go in there?

06:56.360 --> 06:58.680
What if he ends up fighting
with the General?

07:00.360 --> 07:03.400
The General only instructed us to
keep a close eye on Ding Wei

07:03.480 --> 07:05.040
and not cause unnecessary trouble.

07:05.120 --> 07:06.920
I'm just worried about the General.

07:07.680 --> 07:09.360
As soon as we arrived in Futing and heard

07:09.440 --> 07:10.840
that Young Lady Zhao had been taken in,

07:10.920 --> 07:13.520
the General went into the prison
to saved her without hesitation.

07:14.680 --> 07:16.880
Can't you see, Zheng?

07:17.680 --> 07:20.040
-The General has fallen in love with her.
-You…

07:21.200 --> 07:23.160
Do you think the General
is brainless like you?

07:26.200 --> 07:27.560
Interesting.

07:27.640 --> 07:28.760
This way, please, sir.

07:38.120 --> 07:39.560
The night Uncle died,

07:39.640 --> 07:41.760
someone saw Ding Wei
leaving his residence late at night,

07:42.800 --> 07:44.680
but that alone isn't solid evidence.

07:45.280 --> 07:47.840
Now, with him falsely accusing the
Miao family of colluding with the enemy,

07:47.920 --> 07:49.920
it's like the thief crying thief,
he's exposed himself.

07:50.000 --> 07:51.800
If we can get a confession out of him,

07:51.880 --> 07:53.320
we'll have grounds to convict him,

07:54.880 --> 07:56.280
Ding Wei claimed
he found those bandit blades

07:56.360 --> 07:57.560
on the Miao family's merchant ship.

07:58.320 --> 07:59.720
The Directorate of Ceremonial
must be looking into it.

08:00.520 --> 08:01.960
He's desperate
to pin the blame on someone.

08:02.760 --> 08:04.080
I've looked into Ding Wei.

08:04.160 --> 08:06.240
He's been selling off disaster
relief grain to line his pockets,

08:06.320 --> 08:07.440
while extorting the common folk.

08:07.520 --> 08:10.200
And now he's trying
to frame the Miao family.

08:10.280 --> 08:11.640
The deeper we dig,

08:11.720 --> 08:13.760
the more skeletons we'll uncover.

08:14.400 --> 08:15.920
If I can get on board the merchant ship,

08:16.520 --> 08:17.640
I'll find the answers.

08:18.600 --> 08:21.160
-I have to go.
-Not just the Duke of Ding,

08:21.240 --> 08:23.760
the Miao family deserves justice too.
I'm going as well.

08:26.000 --> 08:27.240
What?

08:27.320 --> 08:29.240
Don't tell me you're going
to board the ship together?

08:35.880 --> 08:36.799
How about this?

08:37.600 --> 08:38.880
I'll pretend to flatter Ding Wei

08:38.960 --> 08:41.120
and find a way to steal his token
during our dinner.

08:52.400 --> 08:55.520
Let's hope Mantis Song won't mess up.

09:13.280 --> 09:14.480
TOKEN

09:14.560 --> 09:16.040
I've spoken with Eunuch Ding.

09:18.200 --> 09:20.040
Since you're here
to search the ship for jewelry,

09:20.120 --> 09:21.800
please wait here, My Lord.

09:23.480 --> 09:25.520
What's that supposed to mean?
Are you trying to stop me?

09:26.200 --> 09:27.520
Please calm down, My Lord.

09:27.600 --> 09:29.440
Eunuch Ding has given strict orders,

09:29.520 --> 09:31.200
no one is allowed to board the ship.

09:36.480 --> 09:40.040
Officer, everything is clearly stated
in this paper.

09:41.320 --> 09:43.720
When this ship was seized,

09:43.800 --> 09:45.440
it happened to be carrying

09:45.520 --> 09:47.520
a shipment of jewelry
I purchased from overseas.

09:48.680 --> 09:50.400
It's worth a fortune.

09:51.560 --> 09:53.760
If I don't get it back,

09:55.440 --> 09:59.040
the madams will never forgive me.

09:59.760 --> 10:01.040
Comfort me.

10:01.800 --> 10:04.080
All right, don't cry.

10:04.160 --> 10:05.920
Oh, my sweetheart, don't cry.

10:06.520 --> 10:07.360
Do you hear that?

10:08.680 --> 10:10.800
We just want to find the jewelry.
Let us on board now.

10:11.480 --> 10:12.360
I'm sorry, My Lord.

10:12.920 --> 10:14.880
It's just that the ship
is still under seal.

10:15.560 --> 10:19.280
Perhaps I could escort you
with some soldiers to help search?

10:23.280 --> 10:27.320
Officer, are you treating me
as some kind of criminal?

10:32.680 --> 10:33.880
Exactly.

10:33.960 --> 10:36.320
With so many people tagging along,
it ruins all the fun.

10:36.400 --> 10:37.440
Do you have no sense of propriety?

10:37.520 --> 10:39.080
I wouldn't dare, My Lord.

10:39.160 --> 10:40.480
But we're in a difficult position.

10:44.800 --> 10:46.680
-Is it easier now?
-Well…

10:47.560 --> 10:49.960
How about this, he alone will go with you

10:50.040 --> 10:52.120
and guide you to
the cargo hold to search for it.

10:52.200 --> 10:54.560
One incense stick's time
should be more than enough, right?

10:55.640 --> 10:57.280
Fine. Come on.

11:00.960 --> 11:01.960
People call him a handsome general.

11:02.640 --> 11:03.800
More like a lecherous scoundrel.

11:05.840 --> 11:07.000
This way, My Lord.

11:07.800 --> 11:10.280
Young Lady Zhao, have you
had enough of this seductive act?

11:10.360 --> 11:11.520
Even real married couples

11:11.600 --> 11:13.240
don't cling to each other all the time.

11:13.960 --> 11:16.080
My Lord, you're usually so composed,

11:16.160 --> 11:19.520
but when it comes
to acting out flirtation and romance,

11:19.600 --> 11:20.760
you seem like a complete novice.

11:21.720 --> 11:24.080
Real married couples
are respectful and reserved,

11:24.160 --> 11:26.160
but lovers are different.

11:26.240 --> 11:28.120
They hold onto each other constantly,

11:28.200 --> 11:31.120
and never take their eyes off one another.

11:46.680 --> 11:47.800
Is this convincing enough?

11:49.080 --> 11:51.720
You're quite the quick learner.

12:06.600 --> 12:08.200
As if pulling the night shift
wasn't bad enough,

12:08.280 --> 12:10.280
but now I have to watch this?

12:11.040 --> 12:12.680
At least they can hug to stay warm.

12:13.200 --> 12:14.200
What about me?

12:20.360 --> 12:21.800
This ship has a draft of fifteen feet.

12:22.480 --> 12:24.200
On the stretch of shallow water
my uncle traveled,

12:24.840 --> 12:27.080
it would've certainly run aground
if it had actually made the journey.

12:31.360 --> 12:32.880
The ship is this unstable

12:33.640 --> 12:35.920
because someone deliberately
removed the ballast.

12:36.640 --> 12:38.800
Ding Wei's attempt to cover up
the truth is undeniable.

12:40.640 --> 12:43.040
-It's not enough.
-Not enough?

12:43.120 --> 12:45.440
My Lord, half an incense stick is gone.

12:46.120 --> 12:48.400
Don't you think you've admired
the sea and moonlight enough by now?

12:48.480 --> 12:50.800
It's time to actually
look for the jewelry.

12:50.880 --> 12:52.280
Where's the cargo hold? Lead the way.

12:54.120 --> 12:56.320
My Lord, please hurry and find it.
I need to report back.

13:00.680 --> 13:02.120
If anyone comes later,

13:02.200 --> 13:04.200
I'll draw them away. Get off the ship
when they aren't looking.

13:04.280 --> 13:05.440
Got it.

13:29.040 --> 13:30.560
These fruits are covered in mold.

13:35.000 --> 13:36.200
Even this bronze brazier
has spots of corrosion.

13:37.600 --> 13:40.920
But those bandit blades
only had bloodstains,

13:41.000 --> 13:41.840
no signs of corrosion.

13:44.480 --> 13:47.080
It doesn't matter. None of it matters.

13:50.440 --> 13:51.440
Chief.

13:53.000 --> 13:54.000
Who's up there?

13:54.640 --> 13:55.520
Lord Song and a courtesan.

13:55.600 --> 13:57.520
They wanted to look
for jewelry in the cargo hold.

13:58.040 --> 13:59.280
Who permitted you to let them in?

13:59.360 --> 14:01.120
They had Eunuch Ding's
written order and token.

14:01.200 --> 14:02.360
Useless fools!

14:03.320 --> 14:05.200
-You lot, come with me!
-Yes, sir!

14:07.600 --> 14:08.840
Even the tea bricks have mold.

14:09.520 --> 14:12.080
This proves that the blades
were never on the ship,

14:12.160 --> 14:13.080
they were planted later.

14:15.280 --> 14:16.800
All of this can be used as evidence.

14:17.720 --> 14:18.960
Song Mo…

14:27.440 --> 14:28.720
A woman can be just as capable as any man.

14:36.120 --> 14:37.920
In books, there is beauty to be found.

14:42.800 --> 14:43.800
It was him.

14:54.080 --> 14:55.240
Someone's here.

15:04.400 --> 15:05.400
Stay on guard!

15:07.600 --> 15:09.200
If anyone comes out through this passage,

15:09.880 --> 15:12.040
-kill them on sight.
-Yes, sir!

15:12.120 --> 15:13.080
But that's Lord Song.

15:15.600 --> 15:19.200
I said kill them on sight!

15:23.600 --> 15:24.880
You few, go!

16:08.320 --> 16:09.480
They're over there!

16:12.920 --> 16:14.320
Get them!

16:17.760 --> 16:18.600
Give me the bow.

16:41.400 --> 16:42.840
Jump!

16:55.880 --> 16:58.880
My Lord, Song Mo boarded
the ship with a woman

16:58.960 --> 16:59.880
and went straight for the helm.

16:59.960 --> 17:01.640
They're obviously looking for clues.

17:01.720 --> 17:04.760
My Lord, when we planted those blades,
it was done too hastily.

17:04.839 --> 17:07.280
I'm afraid the ship won't
hold up under scrutiny.

17:08.599 --> 17:12.760
Could they have found some evidence?

17:16.839 --> 17:18.560
What if I can get Dou Zhao to testify

17:18.640 --> 17:22.280
that the treasonous acts were
all Miao An Su's doing?

17:23.319 --> 17:24.680
Well then,

17:25.480 --> 17:27.240
I'll report it to His Majesty

17:27.839 --> 17:30.440
and credit you for your service.

17:33.040 --> 17:35.480
Oh, no! I've been tricked!

17:35.560 --> 17:38.240
Eunuch Wang has arrived
at the Judicial Office.

17:38.320 --> 17:39.840
He has asked to see you at once.

17:42.560 --> 17:44.480
-You may go.
-Yes, sir.

17:46.600 --> 17:48.640
I can't go, I can't go!

17:48.720 --> 17:52.440
Listen, hurry home
and gather my valuables.

17:52.520 --> 17:53.800
Get a carriage ready. I have to go.

17:54.480 --> 17:56.520
-Go, now!
-Yes, sir!

17:58.840 --> 18:00.040
This is bad, this is bad.

18:29.440 --> 18:30.760
You're badly injured.

18:30.840 --> 18:32.200
It's just a scrape.

18:33.000 --> 18:34.040
The arrow didn't even stay in.

18:37.360 --> 18:38.400
I'll help you with the bandage.

18:40.000 --> 18:41.000
It's fine.

18:41.640 --> 18:42.640
I've always handled it myself.

18:43.400 --> 18:44.360
This won't do.

18:45.200 --> 18:46.240
Trust me.

18:54.200 --> 18:55.320
Come on.

18:59.240 --> 19:00.400
Are you feeling shy?

19:02.520 --> 19:03.400
Why would I be shy?

19:09.560 --> 19:11.040
Hang in there.

19:11.120 --> 19:13.560
If it gets too painful, just scream.

19:17.840 --> 19:19.160
The Tale of the Silken Robe

19:20.400 --> 19:21.920
Young Lady Zhao,

19:22.000 --> 19:23.320
have you watched it before?

19:24.840 --> 19:27.480
Bravo! Bravo!

19:38.960 --> 19:40.880
He took another arrow for me.

19:41.560 --> 19:43.960
But this time, neither of us died.

19:47.960 --> 19:49.080
No, I haven't.

19:56.000 --> 19:58.720
Anyway, you didn't board the ship
to look for evidence,

19:59.400 --> 20:01.520
you must have known
Ding Wei was faking things.

20:01.600 --> 20:03.040
So why didn't you just arrest him?

20:03.120 --> 20:04.840
Why go along with this act?

20:04.920 --> 20:07.200
A petty figure like Ding Wei isn't capable

20:07.280 --> 20:09.560
of orchestrating
the murder of the Duke of Ding.

20:09.640 --> 20:11.200
Look at the archers on the ship today.

20:11.800 --> 20:14.400
They're well-trained,
far beyond ordinary soldiers.

20:15.080 --> 20:17.920
There's definitely a more powerful
mastermind behind this.

20:18.000 --> 20:19.720
Ding Wei is just a pawn.

20:20.800 --> 20:22.840
So, you're using this to
lure the mastermind out.

20:24.040 --> 20:26.440
Knowing he's caught,
Ding Wei will try to escape.

20:26.520 --> 20:27.640
We have to hurry back.

20:29.000 --> 20:31.840
Don't worry. I'm counting on him to run.

20:35.960 --> 20:38.240
My Lord, I've packed everything.
No one in the residence was alerted.

20:38.320 --> 20:39.720
Good.

20:39.800 --> 20:40.800
My Lord.

20:41.360 --> 20:42.720
Which direction should we take?

20:43.280 --> 20:45.360
Any direction is fine, just get moving!

20:49.080 --> 20:50.240
Go, go!

20:52.960 --> 20:54.320
M-my Lord!

20:54.400 --> 20:55.400
Why did you stop?

20:57.680 --> 20:58.960
Turn around!

21:00.240 --> 21:01.560
Hurry!

21:13.240 --> 21:14.680
Am I seeing things now?

21:14.760 --> 21:17.040
Why are there two of him?

21:35.640 --> 21:36.960
Su Su!

21:40.960 --> 21:43.080
Young Lady Zhao said
if she doesn't return by morning,

21:43.160 --> 21:44.880
I'm to get you out first. Let's go.

21:46.000 --> 21:47.560
Easy.

21:50.080 --> 21:52.080
How dare you try to break her out of jail!

21:59.560 --> 22:00.760
Stop!

22:02.880 --> 22:03.760
Ding Wei was apprehended
while attempting to flee

22:03.840 --> 22:06.040
after being found guilty
of fabricating evidence.

22:06.120 --> 22:08.560
This case has been transferred to
the Criminal Investigation Service.

22:08.640 --> 22:11.200
But, My Lord,
this woman has signed a confession.

22:11.280 --> 22:12.200
We have no authority to release her.

22:12.920 --> 22:15.160
You're a special kind of idiot,
aren't you?

22:15.760 --> 22:17.400
If she signed a confession,

22:17.480 --> 22:18.760
there's definitely a prepared
retraction letter as well.

22:18.840 --> 22:20.480
If you don't release her now,

22:20.560 --> 22:22.000
are you going to be complicit
in Ding Wei's crimes?

22:24.080 --> 22:25.200
Let her go now!

22:29.280 --> 22:31.200
Are you all right? Let me see.

22:31.760 --> 22:32.640
I'm fine.

22:35.920 --> 22:37.320
Thank goodness your hands are fine.

22:38.000 --> 22:38.920
Zhao,

22:39.880 --> 22:41.160
I didn't betray you.

22:41.240 --> 22:42.480
I know.

22:43.120 --> 22:45.120
The Miao family's merchant ship
is no longer under suspicion.

22:45.720 --> 22:46.920
You don't need to take the blame anymore.

22:47.600 --> 22:49.640
Come on, I'll take you home.

22:51.120 --> 22:51.960
Come.

23:02.600 --> 23:03.760
-Stay back!
-Young Lady!

23:05.720 --> 23:07.760
Or I'll kill her now!

23:10.640 --> 23:13.160
STRONG FOUNDATIONS ENSURE
NATIONAL STABILITY

23:24.160 --> 23:27.320
The Duke of Ding's case
is far too complicated.

23:28.120 --> 23:29.400
From the Maritime Trade Office

23:29.480 --> 23:32.600
to the Judicial Office
and the Provincial Administration,

23:32.680 --> 23:34.200
everyone has been under immense pressure

23:34.280 --> 23:37.320
to wrap this case up quickly!

23:37.400 --> 23:38.560
Where are your men now?

23:38.640 --> 23:41.200
They were just throwing
their weight around here the other day.

23:41.920 --> 23:44.600
How come not a single one
is here to save you?

23:44.680 --> 23:46.680
Is your life really that worthless?

23:47.400 --> 23:50.480
I was just too desperate

23:50.560 --> 23:52.960
and ended up believing their lies.

23:53.040 --> 23:55.600
But the Miao family has been arrested.

23:55.680 --> 23:56.880
If we release them now,

23:56.960 --> 23:59.320
where would that leave the dignity
of the government offices?

23:59.920 --> 24:02.200
Wouldn't the people of Futing rebel?

24:06.760 --> 24:08.160
Eunuch Ding,

24:08.240 --> 24:10.360
you're quite the slippery
eel of the officialdom.

24:11.360 --> 24:12.440
Even in a stagnant pond,

24:13.560 --> 24:15.720
you can still wriggle your way
into an escape hole.

24:18.640 --> 24:21.120
Regardless of anything,

24:21.200 --> 24:23.800
my life is for His Majesty
and Eunuch Wang to decide.

24:25.720 --> 24:28.040
My Lord, your thirst for revenge

24:28.120 --> 24:29.920
has blinded you,

24:30.520 --> 24:33.360
but Eunuch Wang will
ensure justice is served.

24:36.000 --> 24:37.320
At this point,

24:38.360 --> 24:40.040
keeping up the act with me is pointless,

24:40.120 --> 24:41.240
don't you think?

24:42.920 --> 24:43.920
Talk.

24:44.480 --> 24:46.640
Who's the mastermind behind you?

24:49.600 --> 24:51.440
This has nothing to do with me.

24:52.120 --> 24:53.360
What mastermind are you talking about?

24:54.480 --> 24:55.800
My swordsmanship is skilled.

24:56.800 --> 24:58.360
Surely you've heard about it?

24:59.440 --> 25:00.440
General Song,

25:01.080 --> 25:03.280
The Duke of Ding is already dead.

25:03.360 --> 25:07.720
Are you really going to throw away
your future and your life for this?

25:08.520 --> 25:10.680
The human body has
over a hundred acupoints

25:10.760 --> 25:12.280
and dozens of joints.

25:12.360 --> 25:15.280
Do you know which one hurts the most?

25:17.040 --> 25:18.160
This is only the first cut.

25:19.840 --> 25:22.840
I'll talk! I'll talk!

25:22.920 --> 25:24.760
I'm a eunuch,

25:24.840 --> 25:27.520
with only a nephew left
to carry on the family line.

25:28.200 --> 25:30.800
Two years ago, the boy made
a foolish mistake.

25:30.880 --> 25:33.280
the Duke of Ding
caught him smuggling salt.

25:33.360 --> 25:35.800
I begged him humbly, pleaded for mercy,

25:36.440 --> 25:39.320
asking for even exile as a punishment,

25:39.400 --> 25:41.480
but he showed no leniency,

25:41.560 --> 25:43.720
and my family's line was cut off.

25:44.480 --> 25:45.480
So,

25:46.520 --> 25:49.280
when he was being escorted to the capital,

25:49.360 --> 25:51.120
I decided it was time for revenge.

25:51.200 --> 25:54.400
Don't try to fool me
with half-truths and lies!

25:54.480 --> 25:57.240
The Jiying Guards who traveled
with my uncle were skilled fighters.

25:57.320 --> 25:59.680
With the useless men you had,

25:59.760 --> 26:02.040
how could you have pulled this off?
I'll ask you one more time.

26:03.440 --> 26:05.680
Who's the mastermind?

26:05.760 --> 26:07.480
Who lent you those assassins?

26:08.680 --> 26:11.000
It was revenge for the end
of my family line.

26:11.080 --> 26:13.120
It wasn't under anyone's orders.

26:14.160 --> 26:16.280
The Military Command or
the Directorate of Ceremonial?

26:16.960 --> 26:19.080
Even if you keep your lips tight,

26:19.720 --> 26:22.360
as long as your heart is beating,
your muscles are moving,

26:22.440 --> 26:24.040
and your face shows any expression,

26:24.800 --> 26:26.640
I can piece together most of it.

26:27.560 --> 26:29.520
People from both the agencies helped you,

26:29.600 --> 26:31.720
but they're not the masterminds, are they?

26:32.640 --> 26:34.000
Someone in the Directorate of Ceremonial?

26:35.400 --> 26:36.800
Or a royal?

26:40.680 --> 26:42.840
You'd rather bite your tongue.

26:44.280 --> 26:47.520
Fine, I'll exchange your life
for the truth then.

27:14.080 --> 27:15.360
Took you long enough.

27:16.000 --> 27:17.280
Drop your bow,

27:17.880 --> 27:19.680
or the woman you hold dearest

27:20.360 --> 27:22.360
will die because of you.

27:23.520 --> 27:25.880
The act I played with you,
they believed it.

27:28.040 --> 27:29.720
I have nothing to do with this case,

27:29.800 --> 27:31.800
and I have no relationship with him.

27:31.880 --> 27:33.240
You've really misunderstood.

27:34.960 --> 27:36.040
Stop lying.

27:36.640 --> 27:37.760
Song Mo,

27:38.480 --> 27:40.040
I know she's your woman.

27:40.920 --> 27:44.040
I want to trade her life
for Eunuch Ding's.

27:44.640 --> 27:46.200
What do you think of that deal?

27:48.280 --> 27:50.640
She's just one of my pawns.

27:50.720 --> 27:51.800
Her life means nothing to me.

27:52.640 --> 27:53.600
You're lying!

27:53.680 --> 27:55.280
Let's bet on it then.

27:56.120 --> 27:57.600
Her frail little body

27:58.320 --> 28:01.440
is as easy to pierce as a piece of paper.

28:03.080 --> 28:04.160
Young Lady Dou,

28:04.240 --> 28:06.240
I'll play a tune

28:06.320 --> 28:08.760
from The Lovers' Reunion
at the Pavilion to mourn you

28:09.840 --> 28:11.720
every year during Qingming Festival.

29:07.160 --> 29:09.120
Striking with the dominant hand,
slashing downward from the upper right.

29:09.200 --> 29:12.200
No wonder the cut was narrow
at the front and wide at the back.

29:12.280 --> 29:13.640
You're the ones who killed my uncle.

29:31.600 --> 29:34.000
Getting involved with Song Yan Tang
is bound to bring trouble.

29:35.480 --> 29:37.880
To clear the Duke of Ding's name,
he would even risk his own life.

29:37.960 --> 29:39.520
Would he care about
Young Lady Zhao's life?

29:41.680 --> 29:42.680
I care.

29:43.280 --> 29:44.160
I'll save her.

29:50.880 --> 29:53.840
IMPERIAL DECREE

29:55.840 --> 29:58.120
I wanted to use Ding Wei
as bait to lure them out.

29:58.640 --> 30:00.000
I didn't mean to drag you into this.

30:01.000 --> 30:02.000
I'm sorry.

30:03.520 --> 30:05.560
You helped me and
the Miao family escape trouble.

30:06.560 --> 30:08.480
Of course they'd assume
we're working together.

30:09.160 --> 30:10.120
It's not your fault.

30:15.080 --> 30:16.000
Why are your hands shaking so much?

30:17.880 --> 30:19.160
I'm fine.

30:20.840 --> 30:22.520
Being shot with two arrows in two days

30:23.440 --> 30:26.120
would terrify most people.

30:27.800 --> 30:28.800
But, Young Lady Zhao,

30:31.200 --> 30:32.200
you're not like most people.

30:39.040 --> 30:40.040
When I was a child,

30:41.320 --> 30:44.880
I had a dream
of being pierced by an arrow.

30:46.720 --> 30:47.720
A dream?

31:34.840 --> 31:36.360
That man was just a distraction.

31:36.440 --> 31:38.880
Their real plan is to burn the ship
and silence everyone.

31:41.000 --> 31:43.280
Didn't it occur to you that maybe
I was waiting for them to come?

31:59.680 --> 32:01.640
TEA

32:06.320 --> 32:08.560
Drop your weapons,
and we'll spare your lives.

32:10.160 --> 32:11.200
You've set up an ambush?

32:11.280 --> 32:12.840
It's hard to make one person talk,

32:12.920 --> 32:15.400
but getting a group
to spill the truth is much easier.

32:22.480 --> 32:24.960
Next time we meet, don't forget
to tell me about your dream.

32:34.240 --> 32:35.480
Are you all right?

32:52.520 --> 32:54.960
I know you never planned to return alive,

32:56.080 --> 32:57.080
but staying alive

32:58.520 --> 33:00.520
is better than a fate worse than death.

33:04.120 --> 33:05.600
No matter how you torture us,

33:05.680 --> 33:08.200
we will never betray our master!

33:09.000 --> 33:10.000
Very well!

33:11.160 --> 33:13.280
You're all men who value
loyalty above life itself!

33:14.240 --> 33:17.680
But will your parents, wives, and children

33:18.480 --> 33:20.920
survive our torture?

33:21.000 --> 33:23.080
I may not be able to find your master,

33:23.160 --> 33:24.160
but do you think

33:25.400 --> 33:27.640
I won't find your families?

33:29.080 --> 33:31.320
The General is fair and just.

33:32.760 --> 33:34.080
As for the Duke of Ding's death,

33:34.160 --> 33:37.280
you're just pawns carrying out orders.

33:37.360 --> 33:38.400
Now that you've been captured alive,

33:39.280 --> 33:42.520
think about what your master
would do to your families.

33:42.600 --> 33:43.760
Tell us who the mastermind is.

33:44.440 --> 33:46.600
I will protect your family.

33:47.200 --> 33:49.480
Loyalty is priceless,

33:49.560 --> 33:50.840
and I, Song Mo,

33:51.880 --> 33:52.840
will return the favor!

33:53.880 --> 33:55.200
My daughter is only four.

33:55.280 --> 33:57.040
I… I'll talk. I'll tell you!

34:00.320 --> 34:01.560
Say it.

34:12.280 --> 34:13.360
Dou Zhao!

34:14.080 --> 34:15.440
Young Lady!

34:19.920 --> 34:21.199
-Eunuch Wang…
-Are you hurt?

34:21.280 --> 34:23.360
These men are assassins
sent to kill us onboard.

34:24.040 --> 34:25.159
They've agreed to confess.

34:25.239 --> 34:27.760
With overnight questioning,
they're bound to reveal the truth.

34:29.080 --> 34:31.960
My Lord, your intelligence
and bravery are unmatched.

34:32.040 --> 34:33.360
Thank you for your efforts.

34:33.960 --> 34:35.600
Young Lady Zhao must be quite shaken.

34:35.679 --> 34:38.480
Lord Ji, please take her home.

34:40.679 --> 34:41.800
Come on.

34:45.719 --> 34:48.040
My Lord, please come
with me to the Judicial Office

34:48.120 --> 34:50.120
for a thorough interrogation.

34:50.199 --> 34:53.880
A recorded confession
will make the case airtight.

34:54.600 --> 34:55.719
Of course.

34:56.360 --> 34:57.560
-Lu Ming.
-Yes, sir.

34:57.640 --> 34:58.600
Hand them over.

34:59.120 --> 35:00.040
Sheathe your blades!

35:29.120 --> 35:30.200
Wang Yuan, how dare you!

35:32.280 --> 35:33.280
What are you doing?

35:37.760 --> 35:38.640
IMPERIAL DECREE

35:38.720 --> 35:40.160
The investigation has concluded.

35:40.800 --> 35:44.680
The Duke of Ding and his kin were
guilty of treasonous collusion.

35:45.400 --> 35:47.480
All male members
of the family are to be exiled,

35:47.560 --> 35:50.080
and the women returned
to their ancestral home.

35:50.680 --> 35:55.000
The Duke's death has been
determined as the solo act of Ding Wei.

35:55.080 --> 35:57.240
The case is hereby closed.

35:58.720 --> 36:00.000
This is justice.

36:01.000 --> 36:02.920
At least the Jiang family's lives
are spared.

36:04.400 --> 36:06.200
You're here to silence the witnesses.

36:06.920 --> 36:08.840
Song Mo,

36:08.920 --> 36:10.920
for obstructing official duties,

36:11.000 --> 36:12.360
is ordered to return to the capital.

36:12.440 --> 36:13.320
So decreed!

36:17.240 --> 36:18.080
You…

36:21.160 --> 36:25.080
Eunuch Wang, every word and action of
yours comes directly from His Majesty.

36:25.680 --> 36:28.360
His Majesty knows there's more to the
Duke of Ding's death than meets the eye.

36:29.280 --> 36:30.280
Why then?

36:31.160 --> 36:32.960
Why did His Majesty kill these witnesses?

36:33.640 --> 36:35.680
Why does His Majesty
want to bury the truth?

36:36.440 --> 36:37.440
What…

36:38.480 --> 36:41.240
What truth is so terrible
it can't be revealed?

36:42.600 --> 36:44.920
I owe my life to His Majesty.

36:45.000 --> 36:48.360
It's never been mine to give.

36:48.440 --> 36:50.360
My Lord, if you wish to vent your anger,

36:50.440 --> 36:51.720
just kill me then.

36:52.880 --> 36:56.040
But if you still want
to uncover the truth, know this,

36:57.480 --> 36:59.520
not just the Jiang family,

36:59.600 --> 37:01.240
but your own family

37:01.320 --> 37:05.280
and the Duke of Ding's loyal troops
who defied the imperial decree,

37:05.800 --> 37:07.160
all of you will die.

37:17.440 --> 37:20.280
His Majesty and the Duke of Ding
shared decades of camaraderie.

37:20.360 --> 37:23.000
Planting seeds of doubt in
His Majesty's mind is no easy task.

37:23.600 --> 37:25.080
And who could possibly command Ding Wei,

37:25.160 --> 37:27.520
someone directly under
the jurisdiction of the inner palace?

37:29.680 --> 37:32.320
The one pulling the strings,
wielding power over such diverse forces,

37:33.000 --> 37:36.480
must hold a position of power
that few would dare to challenge.

37:43.920 --> 37:45.320
Tell me why.

37:49.360 --> 37:51.200
There is no why.

37:58.800 --> 38:02.680
Since Ding Wei entered the palace
at the age of seven

38:04.200 --> 38:08.440
and called me his godfather,

38:08.520 --> 38:11.680
I've looked after him for 20 years.

38:12.680 --> 38:14.880
If there were any way to save him,

38:15.720 --> 38:18.680
do you think I would let him die?

38:19.640 --> 38:22.480
Every reward or punishment
comes as a grace from the ruler.

38:23.200 --> 38:26.280
When a ruler commands a subject to die,
to disobey is treason.

38:27.720 --> 38:30.440
My Lord, I had no choice,

38:31.160 --> 38:32.800
but you still do.

38:46.680 --> 38:47.880
Get up!

38:47.960 --> 38:50.400
The Grand General spent his life
fighting to protect this nation.

38:51.000 --> 38:53.520
He doesn't deserve to die dishonored
and bear such disgrace!

39:25.680 --> 39:27.480
TO GUARD THE LAND AND PROTECT ITS PEOPLE
STEADFAST IN RIGHTEOUS RESOLVE

39:27.560 --> 39:29.200
A LONE SOUL, A LOYAL HEART
NOW LAMENTING BENEATH THE ETERNAL SKIES

39:30.960 --> 39:35.280
The Duke of Ding's Army has defended
the nation and safeguarded the land.

39:35.880 --> 39:39.600
They are the pillar of the court
and the backbone of the country.

39:39.680 --> 39:42.040
His Majesty bestows upon them
the Yuanyang Blades

39:42.120 --> 39:44.760
to honor their achievements.

39:44.840 --> 39:46.240
-So decreed!
-Your Majesty,

39:46.320 --> 39:48.560
I'm more comfortable with the sword

39:48.640 --> 39:51.520
you personally forged for me
before your ascension to the throne.

39:51.600 --> 39:54.000
I doubt I'll be able to get used
to these new blades.

39:55.160 --> 39:56.800
I came all the way
here to honor the troops.

39:56.880 --> 39:58.040
If you publicly reject my gift,

39:58.120 --> 40:00.000
what's left of my imperial dignity?

40:00.960 --> 40:02.240
Right, right.

40:04.280 --> 40:07.040
Pass them to my successor then.

40:07.880 --> 40:08.920
Song Mo.

40:11.760 --> 40:12.760
Loyalty…

40:14.280 --> 40:15.120
Take it.

40:16.920 --> 40:17.800
Filial piety…

40:18.440 --> 40:21.000
Your Majesty, I will uphold
the spirit of the Duke of Ding's Army,

40:21.080 --> 40:22.280
carry on my uncle's legacy,

40:22.360 --> 40:24.960
serve the nation with unwavering
loyalty, and repay your grace!

40:31.920 --> 40:32.920
How can I

40:34.360 --> 40:35.880
offer loyalty to a nation like this?

40:36.960 --> 40:37.960
How can I

40:39.800 --> 40:41.360
repay a nation that's lost its way?

40:51.200 --> 40:52.800
To guard the land and protect its people,

40:52.880 --> 40:53.840
steadfast in righteous resolve.

40:54.920 --> 40:56.600
A lone soul, a loyal heart,

40:56.680 --> 40:58.280
now lamenting beneath the eternal skies.

40:58.920 --> 41:02.320
No wonder he only used
the spear that night,

41:02.400 --> 41:03.520
without the Yuanyang Blades.

41:04.960 --> 41:05.800
It was on this very day

41:07.120 --> 41:08.840
that the big change crushed his spirit,

41:08.920 --> 41:10.160
leaving him disheartened.

41:10.960 --> 41:12.920
He cast aside loyalty and filial piety,

41:13.000 --> 41:14.080
leaving only hatred.

41:20.960 --> 41:22.560
These blades were bestowed by His Majesty.

41:22.640 --> 41:25.440
Damaging them would be considered
a grave act of disrespect.

41:27.520 --> 41:30.920
The Emperor is cold and ungrateful,
repaying loyalty with betrayal.

41:32.400 --> 41:34.160
Why should I remain loyal to such a ruler?

41:35.280 --> 41:36.360
If heaven wrongs me,

41:37.640 --> 41:38.800
I will defy heaven.

41:39.480 --> 41:40.640
If the way betrays me,

41:41.240 --> 41:42.280
I will abandon the way.

41:43.280 --> 41:45.160
Even loyal subjects suffer unjust deaths.

41:46.160 --> 41:47.800
So why shouldn't I turn into

41:48.560 --> 41:50.240
the very traitor and villain they fear?

41:58.960 --> 42:00.320
This is the permit to take the ship.

42:00.400 --> 42:01.520
Go.

42:02.600 --> 42:04.320
I won't drag you into this again.

42:06.240 --> 42:07.240
All right.

42:11.840 --> 42:13.560
Let's never see each other again.

42:31.880 --> 42:35.200
I'm poisoned. My time is running out.

42:35.280 --> 42:38.520
I only regret that I can't clear the
Duke of Ding's name before I die.

42:39.280 --> 42:40.280
Instead, I've dragged you into this

42:42.040 --> 42:45.520
and led you to bear this disgrace,
costing you your life.

43:08.400 --> 43:09.880
Don't you see?
The true strength of a blade

43:09.960 --> 43:11.320
isn't in striking, but in restraint.

43:12.120 --> 43:14.000
From this day forward,

43:14.080 --> 43:16.200
you are him.

43:17.040 --> 43:19.480
I intend to uncover the truth
and take vengeance on the real killer.

43:20.280 --> 43:23.200
Through hell or high water!

45:13.400 --> 45:16.120
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM.
